00:01:12.930 --> 00:01:18.440
In 1832, an overweight French 33-year-old had an idea.

00:01:19.570 --> 00:01:23.540
He had been writing books for the best part of a decade, but

00:01:23.880 --> 00:01:27.320
they had not received the critical success he had hoped for.

