00:02:49.477 --> 00:02:55.147
fictional world, The Marvel Universe, a world in which characters overlap, fight,

00:02:55.547 --> 00:03:00.617
work together,  interact with each other and influence each other’s stories.

00:03:02.017 --> 00:03:05.777
This, however, is about where the parallels stop.

